'''Medium'''（意為「媒介」）是一個網絡文章發佈平台，由[[推特|推特]]聯合創辦人[[埃文·威廉姆斯|埃文·威廉姆斯]]和[[比茲·斯通|比茲·斯通]]於2012年8月創辦<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2012/08/14/medium-ev-biz/|title=Twitter Founders Want to Reinvent Digital Publishing - Again|first=Christina|last=Warren|publisher=Mashable|date=2012-08-14|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124214610/https://mashable.com/2012/08/14/medium-ev-biz/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2013/09/13/meet-twitters-founders/|title=Twitter's Founders: Where Are They Now?|work=The Wall Street Journal|first=Yoree|last=Hok|first2=Shira|last2=Ovide|date=2013-09-13|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2020-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226202858/https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2013/09/13/meet-twitters-founders/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該平台有專業和非專業的貢獻者，亦有受僱的編者，是{{le|社會新聞報導|social journalism}}的例子之一<ref>{{cite web|last=Sussman|first=Ed|title=The New Rules of Social Journalism|url=http://pando.com/2014/03/29/the-new-rules-of-social-journalism-a-proposal/|work=Pando Daily|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330012206/http://pando.com/2014/03/29/the-new-rules-of-social-journalism-a-proposal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[埃文·威廉姆斯|埃文·威廉姆斯]]和[[比茲·斯通|比茲·斯通]]決定從頭開始編寫該網站的發佈軟件，同時亦有鼓勵推特用戶編寫比推特140字元長的文章。威廉姆斯指，它「只有很少的進度是用於提高內容的質素」（{{lang|en|There's been less progress toward raising the quality of what's produced.}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2012/08/15/twitter-founders-unveil-new-publishing-medium/|title=Twitter Founders Unveil New Publishing ‘Medium’|first=John|last=Letzing|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2012-08-15|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502214055/https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2012/08/15/twitter-founders-unveil-new-publishing-medium/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年4月，威廉姆斯稱有30名全職員工對該平台工作<ref name="techcrunch13"/>，包括一個「說書人」的職位空缺<ref name="techcrunch"/>，以及該平台佔了他「百分之98」的時間<ref name="techcrunch13">{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/04/05/the-obvious-corp-takes-backseat-as-ev-williams-biz-stone-and-jason-goldman-shift-focus-to-individual-startups/|title=Williams, Biz Stone, And Jason Goldman Shift Focus To Individual Startups|first=Colleen|last=Taylor|publisher=TechCrunch|date=2013-04-05|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624080914/http://techcrunch.com/2013/04/05/the-obvious-corp-takes-backseat-as-ev-williams-biz-stone-and-jason-goldman-shift-focus-to-individual-startups/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至8月，他指雖然網站規模仍小，但是他仍然對網站的前境樂觀，並說「我們正嘗試令深思者更容易」使用該網站<ref name="businessweek">{{cite news|url=http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2013-08-22/twitter-co-creator-ev-williams-stretches-the-medium|title=Twitter Co-Creator Ev Williams Stretches the Medium|first=Brad|last=Stone|date=2013-08-22|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2013-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914151613/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2013-08-22/twitter-co-creator-ev-williams-stretches-the-medium|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Medium 於網上編輯時提供一個[[所見即所得|所見即所得]]的用戶介面，以及提供文字格式設定。當文章發佈後，它可以被其他人推薦或分享，類似社交平台推特<ref name= "techcrunch">{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/11/15/ev-williams-takes-to-medium-to-discuss-the-true-purpose-of-his-new-publishing-tool/|title=True Purpose Of His New Publishing Tool|first=Drew|last=Olanoff|publisher=TechCrunch|date=2012-11-15|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804172356/https://techcrunch.com/2012/11/15/ev-williams-takes-to-medium-to-discuss-the-true-purpose-of-his-new-publishing-tool/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。文章亦可類似 [[Digg|Digg]] 或 [[Reddit|Reddit]] 般被投上下票，以及像[[汤博乐|汤博乐]]般被分配主題。而和其他網誌平台（例如[[Blogger|Blogger]]）的分別在於它是根據主題分類，而非作者分類<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/biz-stone-evan-williams-and-jason-goldman-launch-medium-2012-8|title=The Cofounders Of Twitter Launch A New Blog Platform, Medium|first=Alyson|last=Shontell|work=Business Insider|date=2012-08-15|accessdate=2013-09-13|archive-date=2013-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130902193055/http://www.businessinsider.com/biz-stone-evan-williams-and-jason-goldman-launch-medium-2012-8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。用戶可使用推特帳戶，[[臉書|臉書]]帳戶或電郵地址登入 Medium<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://medium.com/@Medium/login-faq-27a103f5b914|title = Medium Login FAQ|date = |accessdate = 2014-10-25|website = medium.com|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-10-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141025170356/https://medium.com/@Medium/login-faq-27a103f5b914|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

Medium 亦於該網站刊登一個名為 ''Backchannel'' 的科技專欄，由{{le|史蒂芬·利維|Steven Levy}}主編<ref>{{cite web|url=https://medium.com/backchannel/why-i-started-backchannel-2e1a14f689d1|title=Why I Started Backchannel|author=Steven Levy|work=Medium|accessdate=2015-07-03|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704135916/https://medium.com/backchannel/why-i-started-backchannel-2e1a14f689d1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==

* 2014年1月28日，A輪融資，Medium獲得 Greylock 領投，SV Angel、GV（Google）、Betaworks等跟投的2500萬美元投資。
* 2015年9月29日，B輪融資，Medium獲得 Andreessen Horowitz 領投，Greylock、Lowercase Capital、GV（Google）、Obvious Ventures等跟投的5700萬美元投資。
* 2016年4月21日，C輪融資，Medium獲得 Spark Capital 領投， Andreessen Horowitz和GV（Google）跟投的5000萬美元投資<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/medium.html |title=社交发布网络平台独角兽：Medium |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-05-02 |access-date=2021-05-02 |archive-date=2021-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604095457/https://www.mg21.com/medium.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

